-- title

JSON Table Example

-- h2

From JSON To Table

This is a basic example showing how JSON can
be used to create tables. It can be used
directly or as a starting point to make
tables more specific to your needs:

NOTE: the format for the JSON is still 
under development and may change. 

NOTE: This is mainly an example to show
JSON usage. If you're looking for a table
in lots of cases just assembling the
HTML and dropping it in a ``-- html|neo`` 
block might make more sense. 

NOTE: You could also make a much simpler
table that is just arrays of arrays
for the data

